data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
The Deck Import Tool will allow you to take decks registered in Konami's Card Database and import them directly to the YGO Card Collector app.
You can import deck saved in your profile or any public ones.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value:
Once done, the from will automatically load the deck into the deck builder. Now your deck has successfully been imported!
Thats it! The deck has automatically been saved into your decks save file.
